<html
	xmlns:c = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/core"
	xmlns:e = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/entity"
	xmlns:i18n = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/i18n"
	xmlns:md = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/md"
	xmlns:string = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/string"
	xmlns:html = "http://www.classesarecode.net/xtml/html">
	<head>
		<title>XTML Documentation - string:hide</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>string:hide</h1>
		<p>This tag will replace every character in a string with <em>char</em>.</p>
		<p><e:lt/>string:hide char="#"<e:gt/>Hide this string.<e:lt/>/string:hide<e:gt/> will result in</p>
		<p><string:hide char="#">Hide this string.</string:hide></p>
		<p><e:lt/>string:hide char="#=-"<e:gt/>Hide this string.<e:lt/>/string:hide<e:gt/> will result in</p>
		<p><string:hide char="#=-">Hide this string.</string:hide></p>
	</body>	
</html>